{"word":"νουθετέω","slug":"νουθετέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>νουθετέω</b></el> <el>(νου-θετέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:τίθημι'><el>τίθημι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to put in mind, to admonish, warn, advise</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>;—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> dupl. <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <el>τοιαῦτ' ἄνολβον ἄνδρ' ἐνουθέτει</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>ν. τινα κονδύλοις, πληγαῖς</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}